### GET all transactions

GET http://localhost:5000/transactions HTTP/1.1

### GET a transaction by id

GET http://localhost:5000/transactions/2 HTTP/1.1


### Create a new transaction
POST http://localhost:5000/transactions HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Transaction",
  "description": "This is a new transaction",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "date": "2023-10-01T12:00:00Z",
  "category": "Groceries",
  "type": "expense"
}

### Delete a transaction by id
DELETE http://localhost:5000/transactions/2 HTTP/1.1

### Update a transaction by id
PUT http://localhost:5000/transactions/2 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  # "title": "Updated Transaction",
  # "description": "This transaction has been updated",
  "amount": 200.00,
  "date": "2023-10-02T12:00:00Z",
  "category": "Utilities",
  "type": "expense"
}